sections.heading: We are a team of industry leaders.
sections.content:
As innovators, we provide comprehensive care with the most contempary knowledge, services and products available. As people, we value each one of our patients and their individual needs. 

Our practice is proudly independent - South Australian owned and operated. We are part of a long legacy of optometry in Adelaide and its surrounds and we welcome generations of family members as they continue in our care.

sections.heading: We know contact lenses.
sections.content:
Passage on soft and hard lenses.
